<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身躯虽小，<delay20 />
却能够以敏捷的动作捕获猎物，<delay20 />
真是帅气啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这巨大的角真是魅力十足啊！<delay frames="40" />
要是我身上也长了这样的角<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />好像就进不去家门了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这巨大的喙正是它的魅力所在啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样就可以一口<delay8 />
吞下一大堆鱼啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，暴龙如果觉得背上痒了，<delay20 />
应该怎么办呀？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它的手应该够不到背后吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它背上的骨板真是巨大啊！<delay frames="40" />
而且尾巴上的尖刺也很危险<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果试图想去望到它的头顶，<delay8 />
感觉我的脖子都要酸啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牙长得这么长，<delay8 />一定很重吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道它的脖子不会痛吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就是奇虾吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然在我看来它跟虾子没什么区别，<delay20 />
但据说好像是不同的生物啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它一定是费尽千辛万苦<delay8 />
才从水中来到陆地上的吧，<delay20 />
结果却被困在了岩石里。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这家伙要是头尾俱全的话，<delay20 />
一定大得吓人吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想亲眼看一看啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这就是风神翼龙吗<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />头部如此巨大，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它的肩膀一定很酸吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原来连这种东西都会变成化石啊。<delay20 />
虽然我知道<delay20 />这东西应该很贵重，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过真没想到粪便竟然会……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">原来这些家伙是住在树上的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这或许就是与巨型恐龙共存<delay20 />
所需要的生存智慧吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢，<delay8 />原来这个化石<delay20 />是你捐赠的啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />着实让我大开眼界啊，<delay frames="30" />
谢啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沿着这个<tag a="110" b="15" />的演化进程，<delay8 />
更进一步反向追踪的话，<delay20 />
就能探明我的根源吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>